  <h2>Strategy</h2>
  <h3 id="strategy-researcher">Strategy Researcher</h3>
  <p>Help us to formulate big picture strategy - what are the crucial considerations that should shape the future of the organisation? What&#39;s the best way to find new members? How can we make the organisation more effective? We can find you projects of any size and no experience is required.</p>
  <a href="#top">back to top</a>
